These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, lemonade, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
There 4 different types of food: grapes, pomegranate, lettuce, banana
City: hannover, rome, paris, nizza
1. the photographer is the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person eating banana is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person eating lettuce is the designer##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the photographer is the person traveling to hannover##1
8. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage         | fanta  | iced-tea  | almond-milk | lemonade |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Food   | banana       | lettuce      | grapes | pomegranate      |
| City           | hannover          | rome     | paris    | nizza     |

