.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, pony, cat
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, emerald, blue, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, november, august
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes blue##1
7. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Pet          | cat     | chinchilla       | pony   | goldfish   |
| Color   | blue      | emerald       | blood-red     | ebony    |
| Birthday         | november | august | september | february |

