.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, drawing, cooking, dancing
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, amaryllis, orchid
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, domino, backgammon
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person playing backgammon##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Hobby      | drawing | writing       | dancing        | cooking        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Flower   | zinnia     | bellflower    | orchid | amaryllis        |
| Game           | domino         | monopoly  | backgammon       | chess         |

