.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, drawing, baking, card-games
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, car, helicopter
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
1. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Hobby           | drawing   | filmmaking  | card-games | baking |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk       | fanta       | soy-milk     |
| Transport   | car       | helicopter    | roller     | train  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

