.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, lemonade, almond-milk
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, goldfish, hamster
There are 4 different nationalities: french, indian, thai, turkish
4 different games are played: go, canasta, scrabble, chess
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the person playing chess is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
8. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage           | water  | lemonade    | juice | almond-milk |
| Pet   | goldfish      | turtle    | fish         | hamster    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Game         | canasta | go | chess      | scrabble      |

