.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, game, cain, oliveros
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, dancing, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, car, ship
 1. the cain-smoker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person driving the car is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | tiparillo  | oliveros | cain     | game |
| Hobby           | dancing  | traveling      | card-games | woodworking    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Transport           | car   | ship       | quad-bike       | taxi      |

