The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, sudoku, woodworking
House: cape-cod, modern, victorian, futuristic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, dahlia, bellflower, tulip
 1. the cape-cod house is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person who growstulip is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 3. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the modern house is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the cape-cod house is the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
 9. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of techno##1
10. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | rock | techno     | ambient    | dubstep |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| House         | modern   | victorian  | futuristic        | cape-cod    |
| Flower   | tulip   | dahlia | aconite    | bellflower |

