6. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the owner of the bird is the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the person who's sport is climbing is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
