 4. the modern house is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the townhouse house##1
10. the person eating garlic is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3       |     4     |
| Food          | pepper  | pomegranate   | garlic       | onion     |
| City         | prague | liverpool | san-francisco | paris     |
